p: The title compound was obtained in 62% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1HNMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ3.91 (s, 3H), 4.68 (s, 2H), 6.69 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.20 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.44 (t, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.51 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 2H), 8.03 (m, 3H), 8.44 (s, 1H), 8.83 (s, 2H), 9.05 (s, 1H).
